high_descs: walk left to face counter top to the left of the fridge
pick up fork from the counter top
walk over to face the stove top
put the fork into the frying pan on the left side of the stove top
pick up the frying pan with the fork from the stove
walk over to face the kitchen sink
put the frying pan into the sink basin
anns.task_desc: put a frying pan and fork into the kitchen sink

high_descs: Approach the counter to the left of the fridge
Pick up the fork from underneath the bread loaf
Turn and walk over to the oven
Put the fork into the left most pan
Pick up the pan from the stove
Turn and walk up to the kitchen sink
Put the pan and fork into the sink
anns.task_desc: Place the dishes into the sink

high_descs: Turn left ,walk forward, turn right ,and stand in front of the counter.
Pick up the fork on the counter
Turn around and walk forward then turn left and walk towards the stove.
Put the fork in the pan on the stove.
Pick up the  pan from the stove.
Turn around and carry the fork and the  pan to the sink
Put the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the fork and the pan in the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Take a step to the left and forward.
Pick up the fork under the bread.
Turn around and head left to the stove.
Put the fork in the left pan on the stove.
Pick up the stack of items.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the items in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a fork in a pan in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left and and walk to the counter on your right.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Turn to your right and and walk to the oven.
Place the fork in the circle pan on the oven.
Pick up the circle pan on the oven.
Turn around and walk to the sink on your left.
place the pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a circle pan with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and veer right to the counter with the bread on it.
Pick up the fork near the bread.
Turn around and veer left to the stove.
Place the fork in the pan on the back left burner on the stove.
Pick up the pan with the fork in it.
Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Place the pot in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a fork in it in the sink.
